<p><b>How do I analyze data from Microsoft Excel forms?</b> Open responses in Excel Open any active form or quiz, go to the "Responses" page and click "Open results in Excel". This will automatically create an Excel worksheet in your OneDrive and take you to Excel for the web, where you'll see all your data in just a few seconds.</p>
